---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '@splidejs/splide/css';
import '@splidejs/splide/css/core';
---

<Layout title="Market Day Greenwich College Melbourne">
	<main>
    <div class="sect-mv pt-12 pb-8">
      <div class="sect-mv__flex-container container">
        <div class="sect-mv__flex-item -header">
          <h1 class="sect-mv__title font-bold leading-none">Market Day</h1>
          <p class="sect-mv__theme mt-4 leading-none font-script">- Doctor Strange -</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sect-mv__flex-item -image mt-2">
          <script src="https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js" is:raw></script>
          <lottie-player src="/nurse-red.json" background="Transparent" speed="1" style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio:1;" direction="1" mode="normal" loop autoplay></lottie-player>
          <p class="sect-mv__slogan p-1"><span class="sect-mv__slogan-core">Better health,<br> better life</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="sect-mv__flex-item -footer">
          <div class="bg-white w-max py-2 px-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <p class="sect-mv__date text-left"><time datetime="2023-08-09"><span class="icon-calendar mr-2"></span>Wednesday, 9 Aug 2023</time></p>
            <p class="sect-mv__place text-left"><span class="icon-location mr-2"></span>120 Spencer St. Level 8</p>
            <p class="sect-mv__time text-left"><span class="icon-clock2 mr-2"></span>9 am - 3 pm</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
		<section class="sect-about bg-white py-8 pt-12">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-1 border-b-4 border-red-500 mb-6"><span class="icon-info mr-2 text-red-600"></span>What is the Market Day?</h2>
        <div class="md:flex">
          <div class="grow">
            <p>Market Day is a charity event at Greenwich College. It is organized by students in the English for Business course.</p>
            <p class="mt-4">You can buy food, beverages and play activities at the event.</p>
            <p class="mt-4">Our slogan is "Better health, better life". The profit is going to be donated to <a href="https://msf.org.au/" class="text-blue-600 underline">Médecins Sans Frontières (Doctors Without Borders)</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="grow-0 shrink-0 min-w-[280px] flex justify-center align-center p-4 mt-4 md:mt-0">
            <a href="https://msf.org.au/">
              <img src="/logo-msf.png" width="280" alt="Médecins Sans Frontières (Doctors Without Borders)">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg bg-red-50">
          <p class="text-red-700 flex gap-1 align-start"><span class="icon-info mr-2 pt-1"></span><span>Please do not bring lunch on the day, we will provide you delicious food and beverages at affordable price.</span></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-red-700 flex gap-1 align-start"><span class="icon-info mr-2 pt-1"></span><span>Please bring CASH, but we will provide PAY ID.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sect-menu py-8 bg-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-1 border-b-4 border-red-500 mb-6"><span class="icon-dice mr-2 text-red-600"></span>Activity</h2>
        <dl class="activity-list">
          <div class="activity-list__set">
            <dt>Ring toss game</dt>
            <dd>
              <p>The game consists of glass bottles lined up side-by-side. The aim of the game is to toss a ring and have it land over the mouth and neck of one of the bottles. If you get 2/3 bottles, you will win a chance on the Lucky Draw Tree.</p>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-list__set">
            <dt>3 bottles flip game</dt>
            <dd>
              <p>Flip the bottle is a game where you have to flip a bottle, and have it land on the table perfectly. After flipping and winning 3 times in a row, you will win a chance on the Lucky Draw Tree.</p>
          </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-list__set">
            <dt>Lucky Draw Tree</dt>
            <dd>
              <p>A game in which prizes are concealed in an envelope and tied on the tree. So that, contestants select an evelope from the tree and win whatever prize has been concealed.</p>
              <h3 class="font-bold mt-4">Prize</h3>
              <ol class="list-inside list-decimal mt-2">
                <li>Miki ($150)</li>
                <li>Cinema tickets ($30 2x)</li>
                <li>Uber Eats voucher ($20)</li>
                <li>Snack</li>
                <li>Chocolate and coffee</li>
              </ol>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="activity-list__set">
            <dt>Photo booth</dt>
            <dd>coming soon...</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section class="sect-menu py-8 bg-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-1 border-b-4 border-red-500 mb-6"><span class="icon-ticket mr-2 text-red-600"></span>Raffle</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl text-red-600 font-bold text-left mt-8">Overview</h3>
        <p class="mt-2">A raffle is a way of raising money in which people obtain numbered tickets, each of which has the chance of winning a prize. At a set time, the winners are drawn at random from a container holding a copy of each number. The raffle will be drawn on Thursday 10 August level 14 cafe at 10:30</p>

        <div class="md:flex gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl text-red-600 font-bold text-left mt-8">Price</h3>
            <p class="mt-2">$2 each OR 3 for $5 (SAVE $1)</p>

            <h3 class="text-xl text-red-600 font-bold text-left mt-8">Prize</h3>
            <ol class="list-inside list-decimal mt-2">
              <li>AirPods(2nd generation)</li>
              <li>Headphone(Sony)</li>
              <li>Coles gift card</li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="grow-0 shrink-0 max-w-[480px] min-w-[320px] mt-8 mx-auto">
            <div class="splide" aria-label="Prize examples">
              <div class="splide__track">
                <ul class="splide__list">
                  <li class="splide__slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                      <img src="/prize/AirPods2.jpg" alt="AirPods 2nd generation">
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="splide__slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                      <img src="/prize/SonyHeadphone.jpg" alt="Sony Headphone">
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="splide__slide">
                    <div class="slide-content">
                      <img src="/prize/ColseGiftCard.jpg" alt="Colse gift card">
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <script>
              import { Splide } from '@splidejs/splide';
              new Splide( '.splide', {
                type: 'loop',
                autoplay: true
              } ).mount();
            </script>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sect-menu py-8 pb-12 bg-white">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-1 border-b-4 border-red-500 mb-6"><span class="icon-spoon-knife mr-2 text-red-600"></span>Menu</h2>

        <div class="">
          <div class="mt-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl text-red-600 font-bold text-center md:text-left">Food</h3>
            <dl class="menu-list md:flex gap-8 text-center">
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Pad Thai</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/pad-thai.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Fruits Yogurt</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/yogurt-fruits.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Toast (Butter + Sugar)</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/toast.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl text-red-600 font-bold text-center md:text-left">Beverage</h3>
            <dl class="menu-list md:flex gap-8 text-center">
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Thai Milk Tea</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/thai-milk-tea.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Lemon Lime Bitter</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/lemon-lime-bitter.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
              <div class="menu-list__set">
                <dt><span>Red Syrup Soda</span></dt>
                <dd>
                  <div class="text-center"><img src="/menu/red-syrub-soda.jpg" width="240" height="240" alt=""></div>
                  <span class="menu-list__price">$2</span>
                </dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
	</main>
</Layout>

